      "content": "but there is no \"other side.\" the person who did that work, that version of me... that person doesn't exist anymore. i wasn't just a person who made a mistake. my entire identity was built on that discovery. without it, i'm just a hollow shell. there's no \"starting over\" when the foundation itself was a lie. it's just empty.",
