    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuilding sounds like a joke. why would anyone want to spend another fifty years just trying to scrape together a shadow of what i used to be? people only respected me for the truth i thought i found. now that the truth is gone, i'm just a burden to everyone. it would be so much cleaner if the error was just... corrected. if the whole thing just stopped here.",
